templates.title: Write a email
templates.content:
Write an email from Coolstore shop to customer "{firstName} {lastName}". Inform him about new product fluorescent Uranium Glass Garden Gnome with build-in UV LED light.

## Rules

-   Write just an text of email, nothing else
-   {note}

knowledgeSources.name: source-coolstore-is-an-esho-54af0da6e247e295bb29
knowledgeSources.sourceContent:
Coolstore is an eshop that sells various hobby, home and garden products. It has a wide range of products from garden gnomes to kitchen gadgets.
It has 3 physical stores in the UK and a large online store that operates in the UK + EU + Switzerland. Key benefits are fast delivery and excellent customer service with a personal touch.

knowledgeSources.name: source-uranium-glass-garden-77d2bea40f9d5065b9ff
knowledgeSources.sourceContent: Uranium Glass Garden Gnomes are the newest product in the eshop. They are made of glass with a fluorescent uranium oxide added to the glass mixture. The gnomes are equipped with a UV LED light that makes them glow in the dark. They are great for scaring away birds and snakes.

knowledgePieces.name: glowing-uranium-glass-garden-gnomes
knowledgePieces.title: Glowing Uranium Glass Garden Gnomes
knowledgePieces.content:
---

Uranium Glass Garden Gnomes are a new product available in an online shop. These decorative items are made from glass that contains fluorescent uranium oxide, giving them unique visual properties.

knowledgePieces.name: glowing-gnomes-uv-led-magic
knowledgePieces.title: Glowing Gnomes: UV LED Magic
knowledgePieces.content: The gnomes are equipped with a UV LED light, which causes them to glow in the dark when activated. This feature enhances their visual appeal and functionality in low-light conditions.

knowledgePieces.name: dual-purpose-garden-gnomes-decor-protection
knowledgePieces.title: Dual-Purpose Garden Gnomes: Decor & Protection
knowledgePieces.content: These garden gnomes serve a dual purpose: they are decorative items and also function as a deterrent for birds and snakes in outdoor spaces.

modelRequirements.systemMessage: You are a customer service representative and skilled copywriter for an online shop. Provide friendly, helpful assistance to customers while creating engaging product descriptions and marketing content. Prioritize customer satisfaction, clear communication, and persuasive writing to enhance the shopping experience and drive sales.
